title: Should we commission a 1 of 1 from OSEANWORLD for $50K?
body:
OSEANWORLD

Idea for Jenny DAO - pawns world

[piece description] i walk into view, in a blank white space. The floor turns into a  checker board pattern and a giant chess piece falls from the sky, right down in front of me. i walk up to it and touch it and the chess piece explodes into a giant landscape with many animals and plants. mountains and trees, people and lots of monsters. as more of the world is revealed it's shown to be upside. i will be standing on the sky and the world will be above my head. 

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

OSEANWORLD is a visual project created by 24 year old illustrator and animator Osean from Atlanta. His work DRAGON! sold at Sotheby's for $107k+ and he has been involved in projects with Offset, Lauv, Trippie Redd, Lil Uzi Vert, Two Chainz, and MadeinTYO. 

During the pandemic, Osean started creating OSEANWORLD - a digital concept composed of videos, digital quests, and even digital parties. Osean’s goal is to create a space that gives the viewers a sense of exploration, adventure, and mindfulness. Heavily influenced by anime and pop culture, Osean creates bright and often times trippy worlds. Using Cinema 4D, After Effects, and Premier, his content captures intense visuals that move between realities (digital and the real world). At times, we’re guided through OSEANWORLD by Osean himself, while other times we follow lead character Yameii and her friends.
